Summary: Validating the find an agent tool
Description (Design Steps): 1. Navigate to Kemper Website https://www.kemper.com/ it will land on Kemper Home page.
Expected: User should be navigated to Kemper website.

Description (Design Steps): 2. Click on Car Insurance on Kemper Home page.
Expected: User should land on kemper-auto page.

Description (Design Steps): 3. Click on  Get a Quote  on Car Insurance page.
Expected: User should navigate to get-a-quote page

Description (Design Steps): 5. Select Insurance Type as Commercial Auto
Expected: From Insurance Type dropdown Commercial Auto will be selected.
User should navigate to autoinsurance_request page.
